{
  "text": "A total of 39 sound upper human premolars; extracted from an age group of 18-20 years, were stored in phosphate buffer solution containing 0.2% sodium azide at 4\u00b0C pending uses within 1 month [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "39114980"
